flowchart TD
    A[Entry Point — src/main.js] --> B[Parse into AST]
    B --> C[Find All Imports and Requires]
    C --> D[Resolve Module Paths]
    D --> E{All dependencies loaded?}
    E -- No --> F[Load Next Module File]
    F --> B
    E -- Yes --> G[Full Dependency Graph Built]
    G --> H[Run Loaders and Plugins]
    H --> I[TypeScript and JSX Transform]
    I --> J[CSS and Asset Processing]
    J --> K[Tree Shaking — Remove Unused Exports]
    K --> L{Code splitting configured?}
    L -- Yes --> M[Split into Multiple Chunks]
    L -- No --> N[Single Output Bundle]
    M --> O[Concatenate and Minify Each Chunk]
    N --> O
    O --> P[Generate Hashed Filenames]
    P --> Q[Write Output Files and Source Maps]
    style Q fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
